            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Clodiu<supplied reason="lost">s <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> M</supplied>ontanus <expan><abbr>Singil</abbr><ex>iensis</ex></expan> vetus <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="2"/>ob <expan><abbr>honor</abbr><ex>em</ex></expan> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>atus solum basilicae marmor<supplied reason="lost">e stravit<certainty locus="name" match="preceding-sibling::text()" cert="low"/> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></supplied> <lb n="3"/>marmoratu<supplied reason="lost">m cum <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></supplied> aereis valvis <expan><abbr>aerat</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> adituum IIII adsce<supplied reason="lost">nsus</supplied><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="4"/>quae restitu<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>erant diviso epulo <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Tafel in 7 Fragmente gebrochen, von denen je 3 und 4 zusammenpassen; Breite bezieht sich auf den größeren, aus 4 Fragmenten zusammengesetzten Teil; Breite des kleineren, aus 3 Fragmenten bestehenden Teils: 29,5 cm. Die Inschrift erstreckte sich ursprünglich über mehrere Tafeln.</p>
            </div>
